> # Show tools subcommand help
> composio tools --help
composio

composio 0.1.24

USAGE

$ tools

DESCRIPTION

Discover and inspect Composio tools.

COMMANDS

  - list [--query text] [--toolkits text] [--tags text] [--limit integer]
                             List available tools.

  - info [<slug>]
                             View details of a specific tool.

  - search [--toolkits text] [--limit integer] <query>
                             Search tools by use case.

  - execute [(-d, --data text)] [--user-id text] [--connected-account-id text] [--t
oolkit-version text] <slug>  Execute a tool by slug with JSON arguments.

